description:
The v2 Collections API modify command's replicationFactor type should be integer instead of string.

From solr/core/src/resources/apispec/collections.collection.Commands.modify.json:

{
  [...]
  "properties":{
   [...]
    "replicationFactor": {
      "type": "string",
      "description": [...]
    },
    [...]
    }

  }
}
